{"tid":2339018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許章潤遭天眼監控 截斷社交","createTime":"2020-12-24T10:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T10:53:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d79644b72a87b5a58cd002aa2517c3eb0385cd","tid":2339018,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201224/3SRCNE43KBHGDLMNZ7JPXMQ6RE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201224%2F3SRCNE43KBHGDLMNZ7JPXMQ6RE%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt1CKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=012a9570\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201224%2F3SRCNE43KBHGDLMNZ7JPXMQ6RE%2F&h=329da5ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201224/3SRCNE43KBHGDLMNZ7JPXMQ6RE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n許章潤遭天眼監控 截斷社交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vIZuMfRuv0XjJdq6TQc2-WCV0Hg=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MJE2KIDHFFCCHFWQP4I6D5N7KI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvIZuMfRuv0XjJdq6TQc2-WCV0Hg%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMJE2KIDHFFCCHFWQP4I6D5N7KI.jpg&h=eb48d75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地民運人士季風（右）無懼白色恐怖，探望許章潤（左）。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n因言獲罪的前北京清華大學法學院教授許章潤，近日發文表示住家附近被安裝十多個監視鏡頭。內地民運人士季風近日探望對方後指，當局的威嚇令許的朋友不敢探望，許目前幾乎與外界隔絕。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：揭公安嚴刑逼供 律師面臨釘牌  周澤：憂寒蟬效應 當局更濫權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面臨當局經濟封鎖<br />\n<br />\n許早前發文指，其北京六環外居所外半徑50米範圍，最少被裝有九個監視鏡頭，而屋苑內則有數十個。據安裝鏡頭的工人向他透露，相關設備能自動追蹤路人、收音及夜視運作。許形容自己遭到「全天候、整體性、巨細無遺的悉心照看」般的十面埋伏，聲稱早晚外出散步時「免不了抬頭望它們一眼，彼此探頭探腦。」<br />\n<br />\n許的好友、內地民運人士季風日前上門探望對方時則表示，許家門外的監視鏡頭讓許的不少好友不敢上門探望，其人脈社交被當局切斷。季風又指，當局正用盡方法對許章潤進行經濟封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n許章潤曾多次發表文章批評中共，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"b41b39277e715e1786769d4e0bfd319d4cfc49ff","tid":2339018,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5560ba02fe199d693954c32020dc81342f4eb2ee","tid":2339018,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"正啦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n生活靠謊言支撐既國家下講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}